"Sabbapaṭhamaṃyeva āgantvā samaṇo gotamo āyasmato ārāme divāvihāraṃ nisinno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn24:2.1.11"
msgid ""
"Bhāsitā kho panesā, āvuso pāthikaputta, samaṇena gotamena parisati vācā—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn24:2.1.12"
msgid ""
"abhabbo kho acelo pāthikaputto taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ "
"diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā mama sammukhībhāvaṃ āgantuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn24:2.1.13"
msgid "Sacepissa evamassa—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn24:2.1.14"
msgid ""
"ahaṃ taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā "
"samaṇassa gotamassa sammukhībhāvaṃ gaccheyyanti, muddhāpi tassa vipateyyāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn24:2.1.15"
msgid ""
"Abhikkamāvuso pāthikaputta, abhikkamaneneva te jayaṃ karissāma, samaṇassa "
"gotamassa parājayan’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
